# 🚀 Basis Lead System

Production-ready Lead Management System built with Django, PostgreSQL, Redis, Celery and Docker.

---

## 🧠 Project Overview

Basis Lead System is a scalable backend architecture for collecting and processing client leads via Telegram bot, with asynchronous background processing and a web dashboard.

The system is designed with production deployment in mind.

---

## 🏗 Architecture

```
Telegram User
      ↓
   Bot Service
      ↓
  PostgreSQL (Database)
      ↓
     Redis (Broker)
      ↓
   Celery Worker
      ↓
  Django Dashboard
```

---

## 🧩 Services

| Service | Description |
|----------|------------|
| `web` | Django application served by Gunicorn |
| `bot` | Telegram bot (aiogram) |
| `db` | PostgreSQL database |
| `redis` | Message broker |
| `celery` | Background task processor |

All services run in isolated Docker containers and communicate via Docker network.

